  "texts": [
    "Overall, participants spent a median time of 64.93 seconds reappraising each vignette and provided 1772 reappraisals across 18 vignettes.",
    "Having established a set of approximately 100 human reappraisals and 10 GPT reappraisals per each of our six vignettes for a total of 671 reappraisals, our next goal was to generate ratings of their quality.",
    "We aimed to obtain 50 ratings per reappraisal.",
    "We therefore recruited 671 participants to rate 50 random reappraisals each.",
    "Six hundred and seventy-three participants completed the task."
  ],
